<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Druhá stránka</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #f4f6f9;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            width: 350px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header {
            background: url('https://picsum.photos/400/150') center/cover;
            height: 150px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 25px;
        }

        h2 {
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .link-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .link-btn:hover {
            background: #5563c1;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
    <div class="header"></div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>Druhá stránka</h2>
        <p>Tahle stránka má jiný design než ta první.</p>

        <!-- ODKAZ -->
        <a href="index.html" class="link-btn">Zpět na první stránku</a>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
